    {
        "role": "bot",
        "text": "<p>Here's your <span class=\"highlight_mark\">pie chart</span> showing the distribution of listings across the 4 <span class=\"highlight_field\">room_type</span> categories. I grouped all 230,311 listings by room type and computed the share of each — every slice represents one category's proportion of the total.</p><button class=\"viz-thumbnail-btn\" data-viz-config=\"{&quot;file&quot;: &quot;specificationsEnhanced_20260109_150128.xml&quot;}\" onclick=\"window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('loadVizFile', {detail: JSON.parse(this.dataset.vizConfig || '{}')}));\"><img src=\"/server/rooms/GUEST_ROOM_TOKEN/artifacts/specificationsEnhanced_20260109_150128.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"\" class=\"viz-thumbnail\" /></button><div style=\"margin: 6px 0 10px; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 5px; font-size: 0.73rem; line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 20px; padding: 2px 9px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);\">230,311 pts</span><span style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 20px; padding: 2px 9px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);\">4 categories</span><span style=\"background: rgba(27,144,186,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(27,144,186,0.2); border-radius: 20px; padding: 2px 9px; color: #7ecce8;\">Entire home/apt: 72.9%</span><span style=\"background: rgba(27,144,186,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(27,144,186,0.2); border-radius: 20px; padding: 2px 9px; color: #7ecce8;\">Private room: 25.8%</span><span style=\"background: rgba(27,144,186,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(27,144,186,0.2); border-radius: 20px; padding: 2px 9px; color: #7ecce8;\">Shared room: 1.0%</span><span style=\"background: rgba(27,144,186,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(27,144,186,0.2); border-radius: 20px; padding: 2px 9px; color: #7ecce8;\">Hotel room: 0.4%</span></div><p>Entire home/apt dominates with nearly 3 out of 4 listings — private rooms take up most of the remainder, while shared rooms and hotel rooms are marginal. Would you like to dive deeper into any specific room type or explore another dimension of the data?</p><div class=\"history-anchor\"><button class=\"history-show-viz\" data-tooltip=\"Show visualization\" aria-label=\"Show visualization\" data-viz-config=\"{&quot;file&quot;: &quot;specificationsEnhanced_20260109_150128.xml&quot;}\" onclick=\"window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('loadVizFile', {detail: JSON.parse(this.dataset.vizConfig || '{}')}));\"><img src=\"/icons/viz.svg\" alt=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"height: 1.2em; width: 1.2em; vertical-align: middle;\" /></button><button class=\"history-export-dashboard\" data-tooltip=\"Export to dashboard\" aria-label=\"Export to dashboard\" onclick=\"window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('openExportModal'));\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"height: 1.2em; width: 1.2em; vertical-align: middle; fill: white; opacity: 0.8;\"><path d=\"M3 13h8V3H3v10zm0 8h8v-6H3v6zm10 0h8V11h-8v10zm0-18v6h8V3h-8z\"/></svg></button></div>",
