    {
        "role": "user",
        "text": "Let's focus on New York City. What are the top 15 most expensive neighbourhoods in NYC based on average listing price ?",
        "created_at": "2026-01-09 15:01:19.553984+00"
    },
    {
        "role": "bot",
        "text": "<p>To answer this, I filtered the dataset down to <strong>42,756 New York City listings</strong>, computed the average <span class=\"highlight_field\">price</span> per <span class=\"highlight_field\">neighbourhood</span>, and kept only the top 15.</p><p>The result is a <span class=\"highlight_mark\">bar chart</span> where each bar represents a neighbourhood, and the height indicates the average listing price. The <span class=\"highlight_channels\">color</span> also encodes <span class=\"highlight_field\">price</span> using a Viridis palette so differences are easy to spot at a glance.</p><button class=\"viz-thumbnail-btn\" data-viz-config=\"{&quot;file&quot;: &quot;specificationsEnhanced_20260109_150048.xml&quot;}\" onclick=\"window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('loadVizFile', {detail: JSON.parse(this.dataset.vizConfig || '{}')}));\"><img src=\"/server/rooms/GUEST_ROOM_TOKEN/artifacts/specificationsEnhanced_20260109_150048.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"\" class=\"viz-thumbnail\" /></button><div style=\"margin: 6px 0 10px; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 5px; font-size: 0.73rem; line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 20px; padding: 2px 9px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);\">42,756 NYC pts</span><span style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 20px; padding: 2px 9px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);\">15 neighborhoods</span><span style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 20px; padding: 2px 9px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);\">price: $281 \u2013 $800</span><span style=\"background: rgba(27,144,186,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(27,144,186,0.2); border-radius: 20px; padding: 2px 9px; color: #7ecce8;\">Top: Fort Wadsworth ($800)</span><span style=\"background: rgba(27,144,186,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(27,144,186,0.2); border-radius: 20px; padding: 2px 9px; color: #7ecce8;\">2nd: Tribeca ($477)</span></div><p>Fort Wadsworth stands out as a clear outlier at $800 — that\u2019s $323 above Tribeca in second place. The remaining 13 neighbourhoods form a tighter band between $281 and $477. Feel free to explore further — maybe compare room types within these neighbourhoods?</p><div class=\"history-anchor\"><button class=\"history-show-viz\" data-tooltip=\"Show visualization\" aria-label=\"Show visualization\" data-viz-config=\"{&quot;file&quot;: &quot;specificationsEnhanced_20260109_150048.xml&quot;}\" onclick=\"window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('loadVizFile', {detail: JSON.parse(this.dataset.vizConfig || '{}')}));\"><img src=\"/icons/viz.svg\" alt=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"height: 1.2em; width: 1.2em; vertical-align: middle;\" /></button><button class=\"history-export-dashboard\" data-tooltip=\"Export to dashboard\" aria-label=\"Export to dashboard\" onclick=\"window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('openExportModal'));\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"height: 1.2em; width: 1.2em; vertical-align: middle; fill: white; opacity: 0.8;\"><path d=\"M3 13h8V3H3v10zm0 8h8v-6H3v6zm10 0h8V11h-8v10zm0-18v6h8V3h-8z\"/></svg></button></div>",
