        "text": "<p>Here\u2019s your <span class=\"highlight_mark\">geographical heatmap</span> of New York City. I focused on the <strong>42,756 NYC listings</strong> and positioned each one using <span class=\"highlight_field\">longitude</span> and <span class=\"highlight_field\">latitude</span>, with <span class=\"highlight_channels\">color</span> encoding <span class=\"highlight_field\">price</span> via the Viridis Plasma palette.</p><button class=\"viz-thumbnail-btn\" data-viz-config=\"{&quot;file&quot;: &quot;specificationsEnhanced_20260109_161208.xml&quot;}\" onclick=\"window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('loadVizFile', {detail: JSON.parse(this.dataset.vizConfig || '{}')}));\"><img src=\"/server/rooms/GUEST_ROOM_TOKEN/artifacts/specificationsEnhanced_20260109_161208.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"\" class=\"viz-thumbnail\" /></button><div style=\"margin: 6px 0 10px; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 5px; font-size: 0.73rem; line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 20px; padding: 2px 9px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);\">42,756 pts</span><span style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 20px; padding: 2px 9px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);\">lon: \u221274.25 \u2013 \u221273.71</span><span style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 20px; padding: 2px 9px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);\">lat: 40.50 \u2013 40.91</span><span style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 20px; padding: 2px 9px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);\">price: $0 \u2013 $2,000</span><span style=\"background: rgba(27,144,186,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(27,144,186,0.2); border-radius: 20px; padding: 2px 9px; color: #7ecce8;\">median: $125 \u00b7 IQR: $75 \u2013 $200</span></div><p>The high-price cluster in lower Manhattan (Trib